 "\n(a) Plot the cumulative distribution function with Mathematica.\n(b) \
Determine the probability density function f (x).\n(c) What is the \
probability of selling at least one-third of his wine, but not more than two \
thirds? (try to calculate this with pen and paper).\n(d) Calculate the \
probability of (c) again using Mathematica.\n(e) What is the variance of X?\n\
"
}], "Subsubsection",
